column16: A happy and charming family home on large level lot in Shaughnessy. Main floor is graced with a spacious living and dining room plus a bedroom, a den and a kitchen with eating area for active family living. Up are 2 bedrooms plus a full bath. Down is a large rec room plus 4th bedroom. Huge sunny WEST facing sundeck off kitchen and dining room overlooking very private beautifully landscaped backyard. Double garage. This property enjoys the convenience of two lanes. One down the North side and one across the West side providing additional privacy and easy access to your home. Newer furnace and HW tank. Effective size of lot is 66’x 175’ approx. RS-5 zone. (NOT FSD) Close to sought after private schools. Oil tank removed and docs available. Showing by appointment only. Call now!

Builders, Investors! Solid retro bungalow on a large 40x109 RS-1 lot (4348 SF) with lane access in hot Victoria area. Located at 26th & Victoria across from Brewers Park this 2 bed (circa 1939) home features original oak hardwood floors, coved ceilings, leaded glass doors and a full height unfinished basement. Great view potential for stellar city and mountain views if one were to build new. One car garage and a fully fenced sunny & quiet backyard. Steps to Brewers Park and a few blocks to Gladstone Secondary.

Brand new custom built home with 2 bdrm laneway house. Comes with 2-5-10 new home warranty. Features include quartz countertops, air conditioned roughed in, engineered hardwood floor, HRV system, heating exchanger, security system, radiant heating, bbq hook up, sprinkler system & much more. There's a 2 bedroom legal suite & potential 1 bdrm suite. Open house this Sat & Sun, 2-4pm.

Location, location, location. Solid 2 level home, 5BR with 3 bedroom up and 2 bedroom down, 2 kitchens, fully renovated and with patio cover sundeck. Home is situated to within walking distance to both schools, Lord Selkirk elementary school and Gladstone Secondary school. On Victoria bus route and to Commercial skytrain and to downtown Vancouver within 30 mins ride. Walking distance to Trout Lake and its community centre. Public Open House Saturday, April 23rd, 2-4pm.

Expansive 66 x 228 foot, park-like property with a charming 5 bedroom & den, 5 bath home in Kerrisdale. Perfect to hold, renovate or build your dream home! This 2 level home offers h/w floors, plenty of natural light, spacious principal rms, sizable den & 5 generously sized bdrms (3 on main & 2 up). Partially finished basement provides storage space & is ready for your ideas. Beautiful, fenced backyard w/lush, mature landscaping & serene pond is ideal for gardening & relaxing w/family & friends. Prime location, close to parks, golf courses + amenities in Kerrisdale & along Dunbar St. Easy access to downtown Vancouver & Richmond. Excellent schools nearby: Kerrisdale Elem., Point Grey Sec., Crofton House, St. George’s & UBC.

Great 6 bed and 4 bath home in an ideal family oriented location. Good rental potential as this Vancouver special features 2 suites with seperate entrances on the main floor and laminate flooring throughout. Walk just a few blocks to No Frills and Shoppers Drug Mart or explore other restaurants and stores in this very diverse community. Just one block away from transportation and one bus ride away from Downtown or the Skytrain. Families with younger or older children need not to worry as General Brock Elementary and Sir Charles Tupper Secondary are just a short walk or drive away. Pictures to come soon! First showing and open house this Saturday & Sunday, April 23 and 24 from 2pm to 4pm.

Solid house on a beautiful tree lined street in central Collingwood location, real hardwood floor on main level with 2 spacious bedrooms; lower floor features 2 bedrooms and a kitchen. Perfect lot to build a dream home on this 54-foot wide lot with back lane for future laneway house potential. Minutes to 29th Ave skytrain station. John Norquay Elementary & Windermere Secondary schools catchment area. First showing at open House: April 30th & May 1st, 2-4pm. Offers to be presented at 6:30pm on Tuesday May 3rd.

Excellent location! Bright and clean contemporary home in Dunbar area. Completely renovated in 2012. Corner lot with architect designed modern plan; lots of light; fabulous finishings; 3 beds up plus lots of room for nanny down. Unique & beautiful West side home. A short walk to the best schools, restaurants, shops & parks. Open house on Sunday, April 24, 3pm-5pm. No showing before first open house.

ONE OF A KIND Tudor style home in the highly regarded Quilchena! The Brakenridge Classic's street appeal is dominating yet elegant in its style. Beautifully structured and perfectly positioned, this home features close to 4200 SF of pure luxury. Greeted with grand foyer and the modern open concept living supported by heavy timber and stone finishes that seamlessly blend to create a sense of warmth and prestige. Gourmet kitchen featuring Wolf appliances, a full size 48" Sub Zero fridge and upscale cabinets. French doors leads to large patio & garden. 2nd floor features 4 spacious bedrooms with ensuites, luxurious basement equipped with 2 guest bdrms, bar/rec room, wine cellar, home theatre and spa room. Close to parks, PW & Trafalgar.

Handsome, solid rancher with a high basement on an excellent 50' lot facing the park PLUS a 3 yr old, income producing laneway house! Lots of space for your whole family and within easy walking distance of schools, transportation, and all of the colourful shops and restaurants along Fraser and Main. First showing: Thurs., Apr.21, 5:30-6:30. Open Sat. & Sun., 2-4.

Extensively renovated Vancouver house. Features 3 bedrooms upstairs & 1bed room suite w/open floor concept in basement. Close to 200k in recent renovation including new kitchen w/ granite counter & kitchen aid appliances, new bath, engineered hardwood floorings & tiles throughout, new windows, new roof, new furnace & hot water tank, upgraded plumbing & electricity, new stucco exterior, 6X25 cold room as wine cellar. Double detached garage in backyard can be easily converted to lane home. Immaculately maintained solid house. Blocks away from public/ private schools, community centres, public transportation and shopping. This property should not be missed. Open House on Apr 23&24, Sat&Sun 2-4 pm. Showings only by open house.

READY TO BUILD! Building plans in place and development permits issued. Imagine your own custom built 3,456 sqft home on this sunny corner view lot! HUGE rooftop deck with views to the Fraser River and Richmond. 6 bedrooms, 6 bathrooms, recreation room and Entertainment area. Perfect for a family! Choose your features and customize to your own taste and needs! Open SAT/SUN APRIL 23/24 2-4pm

Truly rare to the market! This magnificent Ron Thom designed home sits on a massive 14,400 square-foot lot that has breathtaking city, water, and mountain views. This house is hidden from the street, but opens up to a spectacular north-facing view. This unique design captures the best of a west-coast feel as the interior is integrated with a huge, outdoor deck. Unique in every sense of the word! Agents' open house on April 20 from 10:00am to 1:00pm. Public open house Sunday the 24th from 1:00pm to 4:00pm.

What a beauty! Welcome to this 1914 Craftsman Bungalow Heritage "B" lovingly & patiently restored to its current glory! The large foyer sets the tone with its beautiful wainscoting, 9'4 ceiling height & inlaid oak flooring. Cozy up by the fireplace in your comfortable living room drenched by natural light, host your loved ones in the adjacent large dining room while marvelling at the wood beamed ceiling & superb original built-in buffet. The 3 sizeable bedrooms & charming 1.5 bath with claw foot tub will house your family for a very long time. Airy modern kitchen & eat-in area from which to access a lush fenced backyard & detached garage. The bsmt offers a 2 bed suite & a large separate unfinished area which could be a rec/family room for you. Hastings Sunrise living at its best!What a beauty! Airy modern kitchen & eat-in area from which to access a lush fenced backyard & detached garage. The basement offers 2 bed suite & a large separate area which could be a rec/family room for you. Hastings Sunrise living at its best! Open Thurs April 21st, 5:30pm - 6:30pm, Sat & Sun April 23rd/24th, 1:00pm - 3:00pm.

Gorgeous, residential location at the prestigious Fraserview on the South Side with north-facing view. High-end, luxurious, three-level home with over 3,700 square feet and a two-bedroom laneway house. The top floor has four large bedrooms with ensuites. The main floor has an open-concept kitchen including a central island, quartz countertop, engineered hardwood flooring, sauna, jacuzzi bath, air conditioning, HRV, and a covered patio. The basement has a legal, two-bedroom suite, and a theatre room. It also has a 2-5-10 year new home warranty. This new, luxurious, fabulously-built home will be completed by October or November of 2016.

Big Lot in Dunbar, land value with livable house. 9360 sf lot and 4210 sq ft 5 bedroom house. 2010 new roof and top quality material house (2016 renovation). Walking distance to Crofton House, St Georges schools. UBC. Public Open Houses: Sat & Sun, April 23rd & 24th, 2-4 PM.

Solid family home in hot area near 12th and Commercial. RT5N zoning. Features 3 bedrooms up and fully finished 2 bedrooms in the basement , newer furnace and roof Close to Queen Alexander and Secord elementary, commercial station skytrain and restaurants and shops on the Drive. All measurements are approx and to be verified by buyers.

Showcasing a RENOVATED 4 BED 2 BATH home in HASTINGS SUNRISE. Main floor features a SPACIOUS BRIGHT living room with a cozy WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE, a stylish kitchen with S/S appliances, QUARTZ countertops & FRENCH DOORS that lead to an AMAZING sun drenched PATIO deck almost 300 sq ft with views of the NORTHSHORE Mountains. Downstairs is a WALK-OUT 2 BDRM suite with its own SEPARATE ENTRANCE & LAUNDRY. This charming home has a beautifully LANDSCAPED SOUTH facing FRONT YARD & a manicured PRIVATE BACK YARD with a bonus WORKSHOP/STORAGE AREA. Great location only 10 mins to DOWNTOWN and blocks to HASTINGS Sunrise SHOPPING, CAFES, PNE's fall FARMER'S MARKET & NEW BRIGHTON PARK. 1st showing Thurs Apr 21 5:30pm-6:30pm Open 23/24 Sat/Sun 2-4Showcasing a RENOVATED 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the HASTINGS SUNRISE area. The main floor features a SPACIOUS and BRIGHT living room with a cozy WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE, a stylish kitchen with STAINLESS STEEL appliances, QUARTZ countertops and FRENCH DOORS that lead to an AMAZING sun drenched PATIO deck that is almost 300 sq ft and has views of the NORTHSHORE Mountains. Downstairs has a WALK-OUT 2 bedroom suite complete with its own SEPARATE ENTRANCE and LAUNDRY. This charming home has a beautifully LANDSCAPED SOUTH facing FRONT YARD and a manicured PRIVATE BACK YARD with a bonus WORKSHOP or STORAGE AREA. Great location only 10 minutes to DOWNTOWN and blocks to HASTINGS Sunrise SHOPPING, CAFES, PNE's fall FARMER'S MARKET and NEW BRIGHTON PARK. First showings Thurs Apr 21 5:30pm-6:30pm Open Sat/Sun Apr 23/24 2pm-4pm

North of 10th, Crown Crescent is one of the most sought after streets in West Point Grey. 6132 SF of land on 55x111.49 RS-1 view lot. Additions and renovations (2005) give this charming 5 bedroom home (3 up/2 down) the feel of a newer house. Classic x-hall living/dining room with a newer family room off the kitchen create an open plan that's great for entertaining. Step through double French doors to a southern exposed yard with sunken patio that's perfect for BBQs and family time. Walking to West Pt Grey Academy, OLPH, Lord Byng, Queen Mary, Jules Quesnel, W 10th shopping district, UBC, local parks & beaches. A new build on this lot could take advantage of the views for some amazing mountain & water views.

Quintessential East Van character home on one of the nicest streets in the Commercial drive area. This home has all the heritage charm with original Tiffany windows in the living and dining rooms, high ceiling and classic mouldings. Large & inviting patio overlooking your private yard. Perfect for kids play dates and family BBQ’s. Large ground floor with full height ceilings that could be easily suited. Bring your renovation dreams to this sweet east van home just steps to parks, schools, transit & shopping. OPEN Thursday 5:30-6:30pm and SAT/SUN APRIL 23/24 2-4pm

Location, location, location. Rarely available 56 x 107.94 feet lot in popular "Fraser" area with well looked after family home. Original hardwood floors upstairs, reno done, including kitchen, in 2003. Spacious 2 bedrooms upstairs and potential 2 bedroom downstairs. The backyard offers a sunny west exposure with a nice deck, 261sf. for entertaining. Quiet, beautifully tree-lined street, family friendly neighbourhood. Great schools, parks, minutes to transit, shopping and amenities offered on Fraser Street. Please don't disturb the owner. First showing sneak peek Thurs. April 21st, 6-7PM, open house Sat/Sun, April 23rd & 24th from 2-4. Offers (if any) will be presented on Tuesday, April 26th @ 7PM.

POTENTIAL ASSEMBLE for prestigious Oak St luxurious townhomes. Rare find this remodeled home in prime South Granville sitting on over 8300 sf corner lot, offering 46450 sf of functional living spaces. Updates include showers, appliances, flooring & spotlights on main floor. Sun deck for your morning coffee looking over beautiful mountains. Basement comes with a separate 2 bedrooms 1 bath suite with a full kitchen and laundry which makes a great in-law/guest suite or rental suite as a mortgage helper. Top school catchment - Jamieson Elementary and Eric Hamber Secondary. Close to transit, shopping & eateries. A must see!

Right in the heart of the desirable Knight/Cedar Cottage area on one of the city's prettiest streets you will find this charming 3 Bedroom character home. Inside you will find hardwood floors throughout with an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, updated bathroom and a newer roof. The basement is easily suitable with its own entrance. Located on a corner R-10 zoned lot this home is central to everything, walking distance to Charles Dickens Elementary and Charles Tupper, transit and shopping . This is an excellent holding property, development opportunity, rental investment or family home with a future mortgage helper. First showing Thursday April 21 3:00-5:00 and Open House Saturday April 23 2:00-4:00.

Investor's dream lot! This RT10 Duplex-zoned lot is 4433 SF with 50' frontage, and some views of mountains & downtown. Very central location, near shopping and skytrain station. a quiet tree-lined street less than 15 mins to downtown. The house is a 3 bdrm, 1 bath in the main floor. And one bed, one living rental uint in basement. A lot of updates, two years new roof, and hot water tank less than 5 years, nice wood floor. You won't miss this one.

Custom built home locate on a tree lined street in the heart of Killarney area. Super well kept 8 year home just like new. Features such as $35,000 Euroline custom windows, spacious living rooms, a lot of skyline, well design floor plan. OPEN HOUSE: Saturday and Sunday, April 30th and May 1st, 2:00-4:00pm.

Amazingly quiet in a great location. This Full brick house has a very functional floor plan and is a short walk to the sky train and schools. It also boasts an amazing west facing back deck and 2 garages off the quiet back lane. Full ceiling height in the basement which makes it easy to add a suite. You can personalize it and call it home! This is a must see house. School Catchment: Chief Maquinna Elementary & Vancouver Technical Secondary. Call for you private appointment!
